snippet.title: Hey… CHECK in… #PropheticWord #PropheticFlow #11thHourMiracles
snippet.description:
Greetings Beloved!!!

I pray this met you where you are but didn’t leave you there! Please note that not every prophetic word is meant for you so I encourage you to spend time with Father to confirm and receive further clarification either way. The prophetic is a gift to promote communication and your personal relationship with your loving Father, Jesus our Bridegroom King and Holy Spirit our comforter.

🗓 Preview Prior To Possession!!! #PropheticWord https://youtu.be/L6AwfURZWIg
🎶  “WORTH by Brian Courtney Wilson” “WORTH by Anthony Brown and Group Therapy”
📖 Exodus 13, Joshua 1-5, Exodus 23:20-34

🌿If this blessed you and you are led, you too can be a blessing via:
PayPal.me/LadyJereMia 
Venmo: LadyJereMia
Cash app: $MManna1

🔷For Praise Reports Please Post to  https://www.facebook.com/LadyJereMia
🔹For Daily Inspiration, Encouragement and Prophetic Words you can also follow me on: 
🔹Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ladyjeremia
🔹Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeremiabroussard

🟣You can also find me at:
🟣www.LadyJereMia.com

Much love and prayer to and for you all!!! May FATHER Bless YOU BIG!!!

Lady JereMia🙏🏽❤️
